6.3. Comparison between critical stresses for dislocation transmission and FR source activation\par
\par
   In Sections 5.2 and 6.2, the critical stress for dislocation transmission \u963? ct and dislocation source activation \u963? cs are dis-\par
cussed, and the low misorientation angle \u952? is shown to facilitate the dislocation transmission. In addition to \u952? , the activation\par
of dislocation source depends on the loading direction. To explore the competition behaviors of these two mechanisms, here\par
